data.description: This beautiful home sits on approximately 1 acre lot. Newly updated with open floor plan and large family room. Kitchen is open to living rooms, with complete new appliances, paint, floors, cabinets, lights, and plumbing fixtures. Major items include New roof, New HVAC, New water heater, New electric panel and more...Master bathroom and other bathrooms with modern full bathroom. Foundation repair completed with transferable warranty. Finishing touching is still going on,excuse any mess.
